### Core Logic

#### [NEW] [rewriter.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py)

Chức năng:
- `load_group_chapters(group_path)` → list chapter files
- `load_rewrite_status(group_path)` → đọc _REWRITE_STATUS.json
- `save_rewrite_status(group_path, status)` → ghi _REWRITE_STATUS.json
- `analyze_chapter(text, api_client, log_cb)` → `{method, hook, counter_arg}`
- `rewrite_chapter(text, analysis, api_client, log_cb)` → rewritten text
- [verify_chapter(original, rewritten, api_client, log_cb)](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/chapter_splitter.py#630-678) → `{score, issues}`
- `save_rewritten_file(output_dir, filename, text)` → auto-export file
- `merge_all_chapters(output_dir, status)` → gộp thành FINAL_SCRIPT.txt

